{"h7418f0dbg10fbg4bfagaf45g9bb806edf773": ["Please, leave us be. This isn't a good time - ", "c3334ee5-38dc-4197-aacc-4aa55803ff52", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_GuardsIdle.html", "356be64c-e313-49b8-e079-66d5172419d9"], "hefa3e1bdgeb85g4279g959fgbf06b3613f06": ["It's fine, Memnos.", "7ce0afc2-e8f2-4f2e-82d8-27df98acc3d8", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_GuardsIdle.html", "945851f2-5c32-abbb-c4ba-a89a316e0b1a"], "h76b03a93g3676g4294g9711gf99e9f1c6f44": ["Heard you killed the goblin king. Did he suffer?", "7ce0afc2-e8f2-4f2e-82d8-27df98acc3d8", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_GuardsIdle.html", "f6e9b619-dafc-2545-ba4e-b404402dc3ea"], "hd4c5af6bg0ce1g4788g9ea1g7d8aa3bafd48": ["Never mind, don't tell me. I want to picture it for myself. ", "7ce0afc2-e8f2-4f2e-82d8-27df98acc3d8", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_GuardsIdle.html", "5e4c3c5b-33b3-4b8b-788f-091ec2c06cba"], "hb97cb84ag0474g4f3aga6c5g15ab8e56e343": ["Having fun with your new goblin friend? Bet you aren't.", "7ce0afc2-e8f2-4f2e-82d8-27df98acc3d8", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_GuardsIdle.html", "25a87dc4-8543-01ef-780f-687158adbe60"], "h1e1ce2bfge258g4e21g86ddg01640d6b203e": ["First Kanon, now Memnos...", "7ce0afc2-e8f2-4f2e-82d8-27df98acc3d8", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_GuardsIdle.html", "58e357db-7c9d-d0b0-0d02-86a87b12ec2c"], "h56f65510gd75dg4895g97d2g85015c7116bf": ["I should've died with them.", "7ce0afc2-e8f2-4f2e-82d8-27df98acc3d8", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_GuardsIdle.html", "a81c5d51-b5c1-bbc5-89b3-4421f655ec01"], "h799a63d8g0138g45c3gbcd4gc4fa73b1b8df": ["I've had some time to think since we last talked. Can't say I'm enjoying it much. ", "7ce0afc2-e8f2-4f2e-82d8-27df98acc3d8", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_GuardsIdle.html", "8d34afab-9d04-a0ea-6bf8-c473ea7bfda6"], "h9e90d851ga50fg46edg9fd5gbb1e1fabd9ea": ["That goblin won't be the last.", "7ce0afc2-e8f2-4f2e-82d8-27df98acc3d8", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_GuardsIdle.html", "eaa3bc5f-cc02-980f-3bff-42163c7b501e"], "haaa51005g9de2g486dga7f3gda9368ba4da7": ["It was a nice shot, if nothing else.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_GuardsIdle.html", "63137044-4e6d-4835-78c6-212c9c95b741"], "h107f6586g75abg45bbg8c56g3d1c5921469a": ["It was wrong. ", "c3334ee5-38dc-4197-aacc-4aa55803ff52", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_GuardsIdle.html", "82a1e488-ff89-3be7-f60a-f790750ac819"], "hb698d1f8g7dbag4afbg837agd7750a158ff6": ["It was justice. Or the start of it.", "7ce0afc2-e8f2-4f2e-82d8-27df98acc3d8", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_GuardsIdle.html", "cfe2a097-5944-43e3-d62a-3718a7613a87"], "h20d47319g57dbg46c0g8649gbd6a5dd29521": ["This is my first kill.", "7ce0afc2-e8f2-4f2e-82d8-27df98acc3d8", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_GuardsIdle.html", "e91d3c12-ab06-439f-136b-2aaabac0948d"], "hc6f545dbg14d4g44bdg8f4eg460eadafc726": ["It won't be my last.", "7ce0afc2-e8f2-4f2e-82d8-27df98acc3d8", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_GuardsIdle.html", "7d59e1c7-3f29-2b2b-d833-ff67c0ffbae6"], "hd2187988gd5eag4454gb29egc79a1e841bd8": ["Bit of a fish in a barrel there. You could have given her a fighting chance.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_GuardsIdle.html", "5c5f26dd-5154-cda9-29a4-c53925a22329"], "hc0f10fb2g399eg45b8g9678gee1d209468fc": ["Fighting chance? That's more than Kanon got.", "7ce0afc2-e8f2-4f2e-82d8-27df98acc3d8", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_GuardsIdle.html", "53130421-7b03-3011-fd84-8b506e9de8b5"], "hee055eecgfaf3g4dbdgb929gecd6ad79fbfc": ["The longer evil lives, the more it lies. You acted swiftly - and justly.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_GuardsIdle.html", "a3dce61b-74f3-2c88-8e26-11ec18e79249"], "hab33bab7gd710g40dag84f8gda97bbe6f2a6": ["Don't feel proud. Don't feel much except for a big empty space where Kanon used to be.", "7ce0afc2-e8f2-4f2e-82d8-27df98acc3d8", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_GuardsIdle.html", "6dd8db1c-8ac5-467a-a8ad-9025f787238f"], "hb95d1a72g9492g47f6gbe4bg0b808cc97524": ["I wonder what he'd have done, if I'd caught that arrow instead of him.", "7ce0afc2-e8f2-4f2e-82d8-27df98acc3d8", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_GuardsIdle.html", "627df1dc-3462-c41b-7958-90c059954ace"], "h3c6cefa1gc9cag4181gb101g85db40c9b12c": ["<i>Leave.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_GuardsIdle.html", "df94398f-cf0a-d095-880e-6274dc8f7539"], "h7fcc971bgc22cg438cgb094g6f19d97f3500": ["Let's hit the road, Memnos. I'm sick of this place. ", "7ce0afc2-e8f2-4f2e-82d8-27df98acc3d8", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_GuardsIdle.html", "758e7ee2-aef0-8b19-7fce-0882e2175986"], "h3f6ccbc0gae1dg4246gb145g975ba0c1edd2": ["Soon. ", "c3334ee5-38dc-4197-aacc-4aa55803ff52", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_GuardsIdle.html", "15107528-1407-e4f2-7090-175b8039a1ba"], "h2ebe6dc7g838fg4836g8c6bg89de22af6083": ["I need some time alone. Please.", "7ce0afc2-e8f2-4f2e-82d8-27df98acc3d8", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_GuardsIdle.html", "a69ce0fe-ed26-827e-a951-33836d6d4405"]}